room_title: Escape room "Jewel Thief" by beat60 in Gadsden
room_description: 20 hours ago we received notification that Chen Yong, the notorious jewel thief, has stolen a rare jewel. We have reason to believe the jewel is located in his lair. Your mission is to locate and secure the jewel before he returns. You better get going - he should be back in an hour!
